snippet.title: Tapeworm Disco Puzzle Out NOW on playdate
snippet.description:
Get it now on itchio (Launch discount!)
https://lowtekgames.itch.io/tapeworm-disco-puzzle-playdate

The long awaited Tapeworm NES port is finally here and I know you've all been itching to try it.

Tapeworm puzzle disco is a grid based puzzle game where you play as a tapeworm; the local night club owner. It's your job to make sure the fleas enjoy themselves. You'll be helping them collect blood, play bangin tunes and get them to gigs on time.
